> most sought after stuff in the game. Most stuff I have
> been looting is ok but I would not say Fantastic.
> NOW...I am only level 19 Ranger and pulling from the
> 1st floor. Does Unrest get better as you go up in

>

> there and bind there.
>
> Your thoughts appreciated.
>
> Thanks
